        "bullet_point": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "DUAL RIFFLE GOLD PAN: Gold panning pan incorporates both deep and shallow riffle side wall, allowing better separation of gold from other heavy minerals",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "HIGH QUALITY FABRICATION: Molded from one piece high impact ABS plastic, this gold pan is light weight, rust-free, UV resistant and floats",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "MAXIMUM GOLD RECOVERY: Dual riffle gold pan technology allows for all sizes of alluvial gold particles to be efficiently collected without missing any fine gold specs",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "PAY DIRT GOLD NUGGETS: Large riffles trap the gold much like the riffles in a sluice box, leading to a faster panning process letting you process more pay dirt",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "BEFORE USE: Gold pan should be seasoned before use by washing off all factory production oils",
