        "product_description": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "Trap gold while gold prospecting with the ASR Outdoor Dual Riffle Gold Pan for Gold Prospecting Gravity Trap. <br/><br/> This lightweight but super tough pan is a top quality gold-getter and will hold up to years of gold prospecting! <br/><br/> Featuring two riffle types cut into the sidewalls of the pan helping to catch more fine gold and taking the hard work out of the panning process. These deep and shallow riffles make it possible to run more gold paydirt and gold rich concentrate effectively through the prospecting gold pan. This high-impact plastic gold pan is lightweight, easy to use and the most efficient gold panning tool to use today over traditional steel gold pans. It is molded from durable ABS plastic that is UV resistant, rust-proof, and available in multiple sizes. Use the deep riffles to rough out the raw material, finishing with the shallow riffles to make short work of your final heavy gold concentrates. The ASR Outdoor Dual riffle gold pan is the ideal gold prospectors mining tool to have with you in the field whether you're a season miner 49'er or a new comer to the hobby.",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                }
            ],
            "is_required": true,
